{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>最终效果图：\n<img src=\"http://oaz5uxplb.bkt.clouddn.com/blog/blog-shot.png\" alt=\"SimonCorner\"></p>\n<h2>安装配置</h2>\n<h3>安装</h3>\n<p>安装很简单，只需要几分钟的时间，前提是已经安装了 <strong>Nodejs</strong></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ npm install -g hexo-cli\n$ hexo -v</code></pre></div>\n<h3>建立博客目录</h3>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ hexo init &lt;folder&gt;\n$ cd &lt;folder&gt;\n$ npm install</code></pre></div>\n<p>上面的几行命令会把你指定的文件夹初始化为博客目录，目录如下：</p>\n<!-- more -->\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">&lt;folder&gt;\n  _config.yml\n  package.json\n  scaffolds\n  source\n  \t_drafts\n  \t_posts\n  themes</code></pre></div>\n<h3>配置</h3>\n<p>有关站点的配置都在 <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;folder&gt;/_config.yml</code> &#x26; <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;folder&gt;/themes/_config.yml</code> 文件中修改，具体参数参见<a href=\"https://hexo.io/zh-cn/docs/configuration.html\">官方文档</a></p>\n<h3>命令</h3>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">hexo init &lt;folder&gt;</code> 初始化</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">hexo new &lt;title&gt;</code> 新建文章</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">hexo generate</code> 生成静态文件</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>选项</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>-d</code>, <code>--deploy</code></td><td>文件生成后立即部署网站</td></tr><tr><td><code>-w</code>, <code>--watch</code></td><td>监视文件变动</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">hexo publish &lt;title&gt;</code> 发表草稿</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">heox server</code> 启动服务器</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>选项</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>-p</code>, <code>--port</code></td><td>重设端口</td></tr><tr><td><code>-s</code>, <code>--static</code></td><td>只使用静态文件</td></tr><tr><td><code>-l</code>, <code>--log</code></td><td>启动日记记录，使用覆盖记录格式</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p><code class=\"language-text\">hexo deploy</code> 部署网站</p>\n<table><thead><tr><th>参数</th><th>描述</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><code>-g</code>, <code>--generate</code></td><td>部署之前预先生成静态文件</td></tr></tbody></table>\n</li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">hexo clean</code> 清除缓存文件 <code class=\"language-text\">db.json</code> 和静态文件 <code class=\"language-text\">public</code></li>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">hexo list</code> 列出网站资料</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>生成 RSS</h3>\n<p>安装 RSS 插件 <code class=\"language-text\">hexo-generator-feed</code> 插件</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ npm install hexo-generator-feed --save</code></pre></div>\n<p>编辑站点配置文件：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">feed</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> atom\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">path</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> atom.xml\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">limit</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token number\">20</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>生成 sitemap.xml</h3>\n<p>安装插件 <code class=\"language-text\">hexo-generator-sitemap</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">$ npm install hexo-generator-sitemap --save</code></pre></div>\n<p>编辑配置文件：</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">sitemap</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">path</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> sitemap.xml</code></pre></div>\n<h3>通过 Git 方式部署</h3>\n<p>编辑站点配置文件，如果部署在 GitHub 上会自动检测 <code class=\"language-text\">branch</code></p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yaml\"><pre class=\"language-yaml\"><code class=\"language-yaml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">deploy</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">type</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> git\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">repo</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> &lt;repo URL<span class=\"token punctuation\">></span>\n  <span class=\"token key atrule\">branch</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  message<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span></code></pre></div>\n<h2>绑定域名</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>首先得有个域名，申请域名的网站国外的有 <a href=\"https://sg.godaddy.com/\">GoDaddy</a> 等，国内的<a href=\"https://wanwang.aliyun.com\">万网</a>等</li>\n<li>在 <code class=\"language-text\">/source</code> 目录下新建 <code class=\"language-text\">CNAME</code> 文件，输入自己的域名 <code class=\"language-text\">coderfe.cn</code></li>\n<li>\n<p>登陆<a href=\"https://www.dnspod.cn/\">DnsPod</a>，添加域名解析，只需添加<strong>第一项</strong>和<strong>第四项</strong>就 OK</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://oaz5uxplb.bkt.clouddn.com/blog/dnspod.png\" alt=\"解析记录\"></p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<h2>用到的免费服务</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://www.qiniu.com/\">七牛云存储</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.dnspod.cn/\">DnsPod</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://duoshuo.com/\">多说</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2>更新日志</h2>\n<blockquote>\n<p>2016-07-27 优化图片链接</p>\n</blockquote>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li>\n<p><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\">安装配置</a></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\">安装</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%9B%AE%E5%BD%95\">建立博客目录</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE\">配置</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4\">命令</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-rss\">生成 RSS</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-sitemapxml\">生成 sitemap.xml</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E9%80%9A%E8%BF%87-git-%E6%96%B9%E5%BC%8F%E9%83%A8%E7%BD%B2\">通过 Git 方式部署</a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E7%BB%91%E5%AE%9A%E5%9F%9F%E5%90%8D\">绑定域名</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E7%94%A8%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84%E5%85%8D%E8%B4%B9%E6%9C%8D%E5%8A%A1\">用到的免费服务</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages/#%E6%9B%B4%E6%96%B0%E6%97%A5%E5%BF%97\">更新日志</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"path":"/build-your-blog-with-hexo-github-pages","date":"Apr 07, 2016","title":"搭建个人博客 Hexo & Github Pages","tldr":"工欲善其事，必先利其器。在开发过程中用到的软件有 Nodejs / Sublime Text3 / Git 等，参考资料主要是官方文档。","tags":["Hexo"]},"timeToRead":3}},"pageContext":{"next":null,"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Ajax学习笔记","path":"/ajax"}},"relatedPosts":[{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Stylish —— 优雅地刷网页","path":"/restyle-with-stylish"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"优化博客性能","path":"/optimize-blog-performance"}},"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/automatic-deploy-hexo-blog-with-travis-ci","tags":["Hexo"],"title":"利用 TravisCI 自动部署 Hexo blog"}}}]}}}